  "title": "Delegate Sales & Marketing Executive (B2B Conferences)",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role</strong><br />\nWe are looking for a motivated and analytical team player to join our\nconference team and help grow participation at our international B2B events.\nThis role combines <strong>market research, marketing campaigns, and direct\nengagement with business decision-makers</strong>. You will work closely with our\nproduction team to build effective outreach strategies and achieve delegate\nsales targets.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Research industries and build targeted outreach plans</li><li>Identify and engage decision-makers from target companies</li><li>Manage email marketing and follow-up campaigns</li><li>Execute structured outbound calling strategies</li><li>Track response and evaluate effectiveness of campaigns</li><li>Achieve monthly and event-based sales targets</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Confident communicator, comfortable engaging with senior professionals</li><li>Results-oriented and resilient in a sales environment</li><li>Good analytical and planning skills</li><li>Strong interest in business, marketing, and industry trends</li><li>Prior B2B sales or marketing experience is an advantage but not required</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><ul><li>Direct impact on revenue and event success</li><li>Exposure to regional and global business networks</li><li>Structured learning in B2B sales and marketing</li><li>Career development opportunities in event management and business development</li></ul><p>Open to fresh grads and early-career professionals.</p>",
